game.util

Class GameObjectHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.util.GameObjectHandler

  • public class GameObjectHandler
extends java.lang.Object

    The GameObjectHandeler is a class responsible for storing and receiving all the GameObjects in a scene.
    In short you can say the GameObjectHandeler is the Games scene.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Julius Häger
